EX PARTE, MARY M. LEE 20 So. (2nd) 903

January Term, 1945

February 6, 1945 Division A Rehearing denied March 6, 1945 Roebuck & Ziegler, for appellant. Paul W. Potter and Willis Sherell, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

This appeal is from a decree in equity entered by the chancellor after personally hearing the testimony. We find no error in the record and the decree is affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
